bill.summary:
(This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.)
Directs the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make technical corrections to the enrollment of H.R. 3377 (Surface Transportation Extension Act of 2005, Part IV ) regarding the amounts of appropriations authorized for certain highway safety programs.
